        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33051379/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33051379/" class="">第8页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2344003/" class=" " title="Emma汤">Emma汤</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="33051379">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">沈从文哥哥居然也写过关于“思想改造”的文，表态要求将自己对文物的所学应用到社会主义建设中去。读来略心酸。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-10-05 23:25</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                沈从文哥哥居然也写过关于“思想改造”的文，表态要求将自己对文物的所学应用到社会主义建设中去。读来略心酸。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

